<p><b>Question:</b> Can I get a framed commemoration?</p>

<p><b>Answer:</b> Service Honoured can not provide framed commemorations, but may, in the future, provide matching mat(s).  At this time, framing must be done by the recipient.  Mat color suggestions will be provided with the completed commemoration, along with recommendations for conservation mounting.

<p><b>Question:</b> Can I get copies of the badges?</p>

<p><b>Answer:</b>Service Honoured has requested and received permission from the Canadian Forces to use the badges and insignia in producing the commemorations.  The Canadian Forces holds the Intellectual Property rights for the badges, and controls the use of them.  We don't charge for the images, just the production of the commemortation and the shipping.  We don't post images of the badges on our site, as they are available through the Canadian Forces.

